---
description: React frontend rules
globs: ["apps/web/src/**/*.tsx", "apps/web/src/**/*.ts"]
alwaysApply: false
---

## Components
- One component per file
- Props typed with an interface, never inline types
- No business logic in components → custom hooks

## Data fetching
- TanStack Query for all API calls
- No direct `fetch()` in a component

## Forms
- React Hook Form + Zod for validation
